My son.

00:10:50.670 --> 00:10:52.130
Luckily, you're foolish,

00:10:52.630 --> 00:10:53.560
or else this plan

00:10:53.910 --> 00:10:56.240
wouldn't have gone so perfectly.

00:11:04.840 --> 00:11:06.240
What're you trying to do?

00:11:08.150 --> 00:11:08.750
Xueyang.

00:11:10.000 --> 00:11:10.720
Xueyang!

00:11:14.080 --> 00:11:14.720
Xueyang.

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:16.790
